= Ruby/GTK TreeView Tutorial 
 
== Synopsis 
 
This is a tutorial on how to use the Gtk::TreeView widget, adapted by ((<Matthew Berg|galt>)) from the original ((<C language version|URL:http://scentric.net/temp/tutorial/>)) written by Tim-Philipp Müller.
 
